.SH COUCHAPP
.sp
\fI\%CouchApps\fP are web applications served directly from CouchDB, mostly driven by
JavaScript and HTML5. If you can fit your application into those constraints,
then you get CouchDB\(aqs scalability and flexibility "for free" (and deploying
your app is as simple as replicating it to the production server).
.SS Design Documents
.sp
In this section we\(aqll show how to write design documents, using the built\-in
\fIJavaScript Query Server\fP\&.
.sp
But before we start to write our first document, let\(aqs take a look at the list
of common objects that will be used during our code journey \- we\(aqll be using
them extensively within each function:
