.SS List Functions
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B listfun(head, req)
.INDENT 7.0
.TP
.B Arguments
.INDENT 7.0
.IP \(bu 2
\fBhead\fP \-\- \fIview_head_info_object\fP
.IP \(bu 2
\fBreq\fP \-\- \fIRequest object\fP\&.
