.SS Lessons Learned
.INDENT 0.0
.IP \(bu 2
If you don’t use the key field in the map function, you are probably doing it
wrong.
.IP \(bu 2
If you are trying to make a list of values unique in the reduce functions,
you are probably doing it wrong.
